,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T10:52:01.000Z","msg":"唐你老母"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T10:54:39.000Z","msg":"唔係可以去邊？<br />\n有冇問人地有咩興趣？<br />\n鍾意食咩？(但係女仔第一次見會唔會俾個食相你睇？)<br />\n有咩戲想睇？<br />\n你有冇問過人地先？"},{"pid":"9521a413b0f6b8fe7c9bf134dbc2c4342d0eb238","tid":890443,"uid":65256,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T10:57:39.000Z","msg":"很抱歉<br />\n接下來要對你做的事<br />\n全是單純的洩憤而已<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/1__ugCxyV7c/hqdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2F1__ugCxyV7c%2Fhqdefault.jpg&h=caa61468&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/jHi6T01QCqQ/hqdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FjHi6T01QCqQ%2Fhqdefault.jpg&h=b9624783&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1144bbb56212672d9272bdbf7d889ec130d49c60","tid":890443,"uid":140357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"80a92429b26bf3aeec92d34f2716080e0deeb6b9","tid":890443,"uid":197196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T10:25:26.000Z","msg":"A.睇戲食飯<br />\nB.有貓貓狗狗嘅cafe<br />\nC. ikea<br />\nD. 其他"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T10:59:17.000Z","msg":"九龍塘時鐘酒店"},{"pid":"2dc10e0cbc2e90b1a13e2fc34a9d95772a0c4542","tid":890443,"uid":21961,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T11:49:46.000Z","msg":"第一步去cafe先啦<br />\n進可攻退可守<br />\n出到黎發現中伏<br />\n咁懶係紳士咪飲杯咖啡就走<br />\n又唔洗得多錢又唔會用好多時間<br />\n<br />\n咁去到cafe傾落岩咀型嘅<br />\n咪睇下有冇得睇多場戲<br />\n睇完戲可以搵返d bar and restaurant <br />\n咁樣一黎食到野 環境差極有個譜<br />\n邊食可以邊飲酒/食完飯飲都得<br />\n唔洗揀酒吧下場<br />\n<br />\n去到最尾佢又同你飲多兩杯攬身攬勢<br />\n就可以直接去爆房啦<br />\n<br />\n上面成個流程都係保持試探性質<br />\n一有咩唔對路走又方便"}]}